<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="csrf-token" content={Phoenix.Controller.get_csrf_token()} />
    <title>Brotli vs Gzip Compression - Exclosured</title>
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: #1a1a2e;
        color: #eee;
      }
      .header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      h1 { color: #e94560; font-size: 1.5rem; }
      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      }
      .badge-wasm { background: rgba(123, 237, 159, 0.15); color: #7bed9f; border: 1px solid rgba(123, 237, 159, 0.3); }
      .badge-status { background: rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.15); color: #e94560; border: 1px solid rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.3); }
      .badge-ready { background: rgba(123, 237, 159, 0.15); color: #7bed9f; border: 1px solid rgba(123, 237, 159, 0.3); }
      p.desc { color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.5; }
      label { color: #ccc; font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      textarea {
        width: 100%;
        height: 220px;
        padding: 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        background: #16213e;
        color: #eee;
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', 'Cascadia Code', monospace;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        resize: vertical;
        line-height: 1.5;
        tab-size: 2;
      }
      textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: #e94560; }
      .original-size {
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #aaa;
      }
      .original-size span { color: #eee; font-weight: 600; }
      .results {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
      }
      .panel {
        padding: 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #16213e;
        border: 1px solid #333;
      }
      .panel h3 {
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .panel .subtitle {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .panel-gzip h3 { color: #f9ca24; }
      .panel-brotli h3 { color: #7bed9f; }
      .stat-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      }
      .stat-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .stat-label { color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; }
      .stat-value { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; }
      .stat-value-gzip { color: #f9ca24; }
      .stat-value-brotli { color: #7bed9f; }
      .bar-container {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        height: 8px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        border-radius: 4px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .bar-fill {
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition: width 0.4s ease;
      }
      .bar-fill-gzip { background: #f9ca24; }
      .bar-fill-brotli { background: #7bed9f; }
      .bar-label {
        margin-top: 0.3rem;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: #666;
        text-align: right;
      }
      .note {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.2);
        color: #bbb;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .note strong { color: #e94560; }
      .placeholder {
        color: #555;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
      }
      .winner {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: center;
        display: none;
      }
      .winner-brotli {
        background: rgba(123, 237, 159, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(123, 237, 159, 0.3);
        color: #7bed9f;
        display: block;
      }
      .winner-gzip {
        background: rgba(249, 202, 36, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(249, 202, 36, 0.3);
        color: #f9ca24;
        display: block;
      }
      .controls-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }
      .quality-control {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #aaa;
      }
      .quality-control label { margin: 0; font-size: 0.85rem; }
      .quality-control input[type="range"] { width: 120px; accent-color: #7bed9f; }
      #quality-value {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #7bed9f;
        min-width: 1.5em;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .quality-hint {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: #666;
        font-style: italic;
        display: inline-block;
        min-width: 7em;
      }
      .progress {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .progress-step {
        padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        background: #16213e;
        color: #555;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .progress-step.active {
        color: #e94560;
        border-color: #e94560;
        animation: pulse-border 1s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      .progress-step.done {
        color: #7bed9f;
        border-color: #7bed9f;
      }
      .progress-step.error {
        color: #e94560;
        border-color: #e94560;
      }
      @keyframes pulse-border {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
        50% { opacity: 0.5; }
      }
      .input-tabs {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .tab {
        padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        border-bottom: none;
        background: #0f1a2e;
        color: #888;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .tab.active {
        background: #16213e;
        color: #eee;
        border-color: #333;
      }
      #input-text textarea, .drop-zone {
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 8px;
      }
      .drop-zone {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 180px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #16213e;
        border: 2px dashed #333;
        color: #888;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
        position: relative;
      }
      .drop-zone.dragover {
        border-color: #e94560;
        background: rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.05);
      }
      .drop-zone input[type="file"] {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        opacity: 0;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      .drop-zone p { pointer-events: none; font-size: 0.9rem; }
      .file-info {
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
        background: #16213e;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #aaa;
      }
      .file-info strong { color: #eee; }
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .results { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        h1 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Compression Benchmark: Brotli vs Gzip</h1>
      <span class="badge badge-wasm">WASM-powered</span>
      <span id="wasm-status" class="badge badge-status">Loading WASM...</span>
    </div>
    <p class="desc">
      Type or paste text below to compare compression algorithms in real time.
      Gzip runs via the browser's built-in CompressionStream API.
      Brotli runs via Rust compiled to WebAssembly.
    </p>

    <%= @inner_content %>

    <div class="input-tabs">
      <button id="tab-text" class="tab active" onclick="switchTab('text')">Text Input</button>
      <button id="tab-file" class="tab" onclick="switchTab('file')">File Input</button>
    </div>

    <div id="input-text">
      <textarea id="text-input"></textarea>
    </div>

    <div id="input-file" style="display:none">
      <div id="drop-zone" class="drop-zone">
        <p>Drop a file here or click to select</p>
        <input type="file" id="file-input" />
      </div>
      <div id="file-info" class="file-info" style="display:none"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="controls-row">
      <div class="original-size">
        Original size: <span id="original-size">0 bytes</span>
      </div>
      <div class="quality-control">
        <label for="quality-slider">Brotli quality:</label>
        <input type="range" id="quality-slider" min="0" max="11" value="4" />
        <span id="quality-value">4</span>
        <span class="quality-hint" id="quality-hint">balanced</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="progress" class="progress" style="display:none">
      <div class="progress-step" id="step-read">Reading file...</div>
      <div class="progress-step" id="step-gzip">Gzip: waiting</div>
      <div class="progress-step" id="step-brotli">Brotli: waiting</div>
    </div>

    <div class="results">
      <div class="panel panel-gzip">
        <h3>Gzip (JavaScript)</h3>
        <div class="subtitle">CompressionStream API</div>
        <div id="gzip-results">
          <p class="placeholder">Enter text above to see results</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel panel-brotli">
        <h3>Brotli (WASM)</h3>
        <div class="subtitle">Rust brotli crate via Exclosured</div>
        <div id="brotli-results">
          <p class="placeholder">Enter text above to see results</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="winner" class="winner"></div>

    <div class="note">
      <strong>Why does this matter?</strong> Brotli compression is
      <strong>not available</strong> in browser JavaScript. The
      <code>CompressionStream</code> API only supports <code>gzip</code>
      and <code>deflate</code>. This demo uses Rust's
      <code>brotli</code> crate compiled to WebAssembly via
      <strong>Exclosured</strong>, bringing a capability to the browser
      that is otherwise impossible with pure JS.
    </div>

    <script defer phx-track-static src={"/assets/app.js"}></script>
  </body>
</html>
